parcel.description:
ScifiPunks is a limited edition collection of 451 iconic sci-fi characters immortalized in punk form on the Ethereum blockchain. Each 1/1 edition is hand-generated by [@patternbase](https://twitter.com/Patternbase).

Collect ScifiPunks on [OpenSea](https://opensea.io/collection/scifipunks?search[sortAscending]=false&search[sortBy]=CREATED_DATE).

Follow @ScifiPunks on [Discord](https://discord.gg/JJRubUn9my) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/Patternbase) | [Instagram](https://instagram.com/Patternbase) | [Website](https://www.scifipunks.com/)

ScifiPunks is a certified subgenre of Unofficial Punks™.
Only 451 ScifiPunks will ever be released.

⚠️ This project pays homage to the OG cryptopunks project and is not affiliated with Larva Labs.
